==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Strychnic
<hw>Strych"nic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
strychnine; produced by strychnine; <as>as, <ex>strychnic</ex>
compounds; <ex>strychnic</ex> poisoning</as></def>; specifically
<fld>(Chem.)</fld>, <def>used to designate an acid, called also
<xex>igasuric acid</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strychnine</ent>⟦br⟧
